name: Ghoomar Traditional Thali Restaurants - Goa

reviews.review_text: We had the pleasure of dining at Ghoomar Restaurant in Porvorim, Goa, and it was an unforgettable experience! The traditional Rajasthani vegetarian food served here is simply outstanding. Each dish is bursting with authentic flavors and made with the finest ingredients, offering a true taste of Rajasthan. From the delicious dal baati churma to the mouthwatering gatte ki sabzi, every item on the menu is a treat for the senses. The service was impeccable, and the ambiance added to the warm, welcoming feel of the restaurant. It was a wonderful dining experience for our entire family, and we left completely satisfied. Highly recommend Ghoomar to anyone looking to indulge in some exceptional Rajasthani vegetarian cuisine!

If you’re in North Goa and craving an authentic Rajasthani dining experience, Ghoomar is a must-visit gem. This restaurant brings the rich flavors of Rajasthan to life, with every dish crafted to perfection. The dal and kadhi were truly exceptional, capturing that signature Rajasthani taste. The halwa was a highlight—perfectly sweet and full of traditional warmth. While all the items were delightful, the churma was the only one that didn’t quite match the high standards set by the rest of the meal.

The restaurant offers a great ambiance that makes you feel like you’re dining in the heart of Rajasthan. Plus, the prices are very reasonable for the quality and quantity of food provided. Convenient parking is available, which is a bonus in Goa.

For anyone looking to indulge in delicious, authentic Rajasthani cuisine, Ghoomar is a culinary experience not to be missed.

The food in general was amazing, prolly the beat veg thali iv had in 10 years. Being a very particular food critic, i dont think iv ever gone this crazy over a veg thali. The customer service is amazing and the the taste of the food is off the charts. And the funny part is its super affordable. Definitely recommend to come with family.

description:
### Ghoomar Traditional Thali Restaurant: A Taste of Rajasthan in Goa

Nestled in the vibrant surroundings of Porvorim, Goa, **Ghoomar Traditional Thali Restaurant** boasts an impressive **4.7-star rating** from **over 4,000 reviews**. This culinary gem specializes in authentic Rajasthani vegetarian cuisine, drawing diners into a world of traditional flavors, particularly highlighted by offerings such as **dal bati** and **gatte ki sabzi**. With tags like **live music** (45 mentions), **folk music** (30 mentions), and an emphasis on **Rajasthani culture**, Ghoomar promises a rich sensory experience that transcends just the food.

### Ambiance & Design

Upon entering Ghoomar, guests are greeted by an ambiance that reflects the soul of Rajasthan. The décor combines warm, earthy tones with traditional motifs that evoke a rustic yet sophisticated charm. Dim lighting enhances the cozy atmosphere, while wooden furniture adds to the authenticity of the setting. Many patrons noted the soothing sounds of **live folk music** that fill the air, creating a lively yet relaxed dining environment. Photos to accompany this narrative showcase intricately designed wall art capturing the essence of Rajasthani culture—a true feast for the eyes.

![Ghoomar Restaurant Interior](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdkGqStIzW8niScO41SwTt0pfuGStKwPNK3bWP-gBADWwfgnUXQC7BIRgbrn_rKF4ZgIIg_FysOBOz9YBTO3CVLSzTTAMNC__4UQIn_ktBC5rI2vVOjEfoLGxhCSgm5KGoBNxxdASw=w375-h281-p)

### Menu & Culinary Experience

The menu at Ghoomar is a treasure trove of traditional Rajasthani dishes, each prepared with meticulous attention to detail. Signature items like **dal baati churma** and **gatte ki sabzi** steal the spotlight, praised for their authentic flavors and aromatic spices. Guests have described the **vegetarian thali** as the best they have experienced in years—a delightful combination of well-balanced tastes and generous portions, making it an excellent value for money.

Notably, the **halwa** has garnered praise for its comforting sweetness and traditional warmth, while other dishes such as **kadhi** have also received positive mentions. Diners can rest assured that accommodations for dietary preferences are seamlessly integrated into the offerings, catering to diverse palates.

![Dal Bati](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdl7-FaHe06f7kOP4tlJHG_PWw-xenzGhbtAAy8cTka0t31mbtNM-8tJTCOulFliIy7VqU9b5EwS8jmXJG0BhJY8AkGwCwBrW0Q4gNjEw3flRc_pw-FnLv6vI9JNnonvMZahpNORxg=w375-h281-p)

### Customer Experience & Service

The customer service at Ghoomar is consistently praised for its warmth and efficiency. Reviewers highlight the friendly demeanor of the staff, who are always eager to recommend dishes and ensure a pleasant dining experience. The restaurant’s policy on reservations and walk-ins is quite accommodating, allowing guests the flexibility to savor their meals without stress. Many families have shared positive experiences, emphasizing Ghoomar as an ideal spot for group dining.

![Dining Experience](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdmDObwsYJNm93mdiNB2Bkd-ldJUWTk9e8rJ4weP9hNWb5nEBua1hcka8-YJ68eljTfyP2_h1E_gAJzvvgewUGfpOYC8mlNB1iIdfQhlx2tnuNQrtCB4y59MGUYz5YM0Xgr0tQn4RA=w375-h281-p)

### Popularity & Reviews

Ghoomar has resonated well with the Goan community and tourists alike, creating a buzz on social media for its exceptional dining experiences. Many diners commend the restaurant for its authentic representation of Rajasthani culture through both food and music, making it a notable mention in local dining guides. Critics have praised its vibrant atmosphere and culinary craftsmanship, establishing Ghoomar as a must-visit location for anyone seeking a memorable meal in Goa.

![Delicious Thali](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdnuBKisJGFwUGvGZeCgaB8CwLjGNh3RsAF9m_qZkyCeBb4V8RY-MXDG7mmeCcytgooepOhdnTBNNKkj8DVJGF3zwtbLmmaalRPNPRSh0iRRLZtMg0HhrWtijQQ69ncC3Ee8Gns=w375-h281-p)

### Conclusion

In conclusion, **Ghoomar Traditional Thali Restaurant** stands as a beacon of Rajasthani cuisine in the heart of Goa, where flavors, music, and exceptional service come together to create a sumptuous dining experience. For anyone seeking to indulge in authentic vegetarian dishes accompanied by melodious **Rajasthani music**, a visit to Ghoomar is an experience that should not be overlooked.
